24
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:39,000
 The weather was awesome.

25
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,000
 The venue was outdoors.

26
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:42,000
 The sun was setting.

27
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:45,000
