 You look at your situation, the circumstances of your life, the qualities that mark your walk with God,

79
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:38,000
 and what you feel is apathy, disinterest, maybe some occasional optimism, but you feel infrequent satisfaction.

80
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:42,000
 If that's you here tonight, then hold my drink, because I'm here to save your party.

