00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:37,000
 Instead, it must be attributed to a matter of mood, how we generally feel about life itself."

98
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:43,000
 Now, it's important to acknowledge that while the science is very even debated to some extent,

99
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:50,000
 30 to 40% of your happiness in life is genetically impacted,

100
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:54,000
 which helps to explain why some of us are more or less prone to positivity than others,

101
00:07:54,000 --> 00:08:01,000
 which if that's you, if melancholy or apathy is a part of your normal experience, we're going to get to that.

