 It's that we've gotten something wrong.

126
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:11,000
 The logical explanation is we have gotten something wrong.

127
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:16,000
 So many of us, we know everything about Jesus, but we don't feel anything for him.

128
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:23,000
 And if that's you, if you're somewhere short of satisfied in life, if you're wondering, "Man, where did I go wrong?"

129
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:28,000
 Then you're in the right place because we want to help you get your joy back.

130
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:34,000
 But before we can know how to find joy, we've got to talk about what joy is, which is the goal of tonight.

