00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:10,000
 They're Jews and that would be unclean.

287
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:12,000
 They're not throwing any pigs around.

288
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:17,000
 They're just having a good time.

289
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:28,000
 This is just one of three pilgrimage festivals, seven religious festivals, and it's not including New Moon Feasts, regular Sabbath celebrations, and the year of Jubilee.

