00:21:53,000 --> 00:22:06,000
 Like, it's not evil of him or wrong of him or malicious of him to command us to party.

297
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:10,000
 And yet our experience does not feel like that, does it?

298
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:14,000
 We must have gotten something wrong.

