00:26:51,000 --> 00:26:54,000
 I'm not real sure that that makes sense.

351
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:58,000
 Who says? Like, the Bible doesn't say that.

352
00:26:58,000 --> 00:27:06,000
 The Bible does not in any way ever suggest that joy and happiness should be disassociated from one another.

353
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:09,000
 In fact, when you read the scriptures, there are multiple examples.

354
00:27:09,000 --> 00:27:15,000
 I'll just give you a few of where those two qualities, joy and happiness, sit side by side.

