00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:40,000
 And I try to do my best to confess my sins and pray my prayers.

374
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:43,000
 I want to fear the Lord as well as I can.

375
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:47,000
 Like we do everything right, but we feel totally wrong.

376
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:57,000
 Like we've adopted all the right habits, but we have lost the right heart.

377
00:28:57,000 --> 00:29:02,000
 God wants so much more for you, Christian.

378
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:07,000
 He wants so much more for you than boring belief.

379
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:11,000
 Than a belief that will not compel the world to watch and wonder.

380
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:16,000
 And yet leaves them so underwhelmed with this God you believe in.

381
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:23,000
 That they dare question if you even believe it yourself.

382
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:32,000
 Dallas Willard, another quote says, "How many people are radically and permanently repelled from the way."

383
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:35,000
 That's talking about Christianity by Christians.

384
00:29:35,000 --> 00:29:44,000
 "Who are unfeeling, stiff, unapproachable, boringly lifeless, obsessive and dissatisfied."

385
00:29:44,000 --> 00:29:47,000
 Yet such Christians are everywhere.

386
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:51,000
 And what they are missing is the wholesome liveliness.

387
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:57,000
 Springing from a balanced vitality with the freedom of God's loving rule.

388
00:29:57,000 --> 00:30:00,000
 You see, spirituality, wrongly understood or pursued.

389
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:06,000
 Is a major source of human misery and rebelling against God.

390
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:11,000
 So, what am I telling you then?

391
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:15,000
 Like you shouldn't do it if it doesn't make you feel good.

392
00:30:15,000 --> 00:30:18,000
 Like you're only obedient if it makes you happy.

393
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:24,000
 You should only pursue holiness so long as it preserves your joy.

394
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:31,000
 No, what I am saying is that if your obedience is costing you happiness.

395
00:30:31,000 --> 00:30:34,000
 Or your holiness is empty of joy.

396
00:30:34,000 --> 00:30:41,000
 Then something is certainly wrong.

397
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:44,000
 It's certainly wrong because that is not the way that God designed it.

