00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:19,000
 So if your soul's unsatisfied, if your heart is unhappy,

436
00:33:19,000 --> 00:33:23,000
 then the chances are good that you're pursuing joy in the wrong things.

437
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:26,000
 You're looking to the world. You're not looking to God.

438
00:33:26,000 --> 00:33:28,000
 You're inspecting transient things.

439
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:30,000
 You're not looking to transcendent things.

440
00:33:30,000 --> 00:33:34,000
 That's why jobs and guys and girls and trips and influence and pay and a better body,

